{title: Lookin' Out My Back Door}
{artist: Creedence Clearwater Revival}
{key: Bb}
{tempo: 106}
{comment: ♩ = 106  —  from "Bother me tomorrow" (Verse 3): ♩ = 82  —  Outro: ♩ = 106}

{start_of_grid: Intro}
